author: Kate McCann
title: Seven day NHS plan doomed without 38,000 extra doctors, Cameron warned
text: Politics Seven day NHS plan doomed without 38,000 extra doctors, Cameron warned The President of the Royal College of Physicians said the Prime Minister's 'Utopian' plan will fail without more money, staff and additional services David Cameron's seven day NHS plan has been dealt a blow Photo: Lynne Cameron/PA By Kate McCann , Senior Political Correspondent 7:04PM BST 13 Oct 2015
